If you’ve been paying attention, you know Gavi and Microsoft have been working together on projects such as ID2020. 
You know Trump has poured billions into operation warp speed to fast track a vaccine by the end of 2020. 
But now, for all of you denying Trump has any connections to Gates, hold on to your butts!  Because you now know that Trump proudly speaks about his billion dollar partnership with Gavi. “Hah Trump never said they were mandatory” you say? 
Have you ever thought about how you’re going to go back to work once the vaccines become a requirement in order to go back to work to “ensure a safe working environment”?
Have you thought about how you are going to travel internationally? 
Have you thought about anything other than hoping that things are just going to somehow go back to normal? 
You all need to stop defending the cult leader and wake up. •
